      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>meat-free sausages</strong> to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until the sausages are cooked through and starting to crisp</p>",
