    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free sausages are done, remove them from the oven and slice them on a diagonal into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong>, <strong>sliced meat-free sausages</strong>,<strong> boiled potatoes </strong>and <strong>broccoli </strong>to the <strong>mustard & shallot dressing </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>warm meat-free sausage, mustard & broccoli salad</strong></p>",
